      <title>安巴尼家族的盛大婚礼为长达 134 天的庆典画上句号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/blowout-wedding-of-ambani-scion-caps-134-day-long-celebration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3 月份举行了为期三天的庆祝活动，蕾哈娜出席并参观了家庭动物园。5 月份乘坐豪华游轮从巴勒莫前往波托菲诺。上周举行了 50 对贫困夫妇的集体婚礼，然后是一场以贾斯汀·比伯为主角的音乐活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/blowout-wedding-of-ambani-scion-caps-134-day-long-celebration</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
